channel.title: The most embarassing thing that EVER happend to you
channel.description:
Well,just post the most embarassing thing that happend to you.
Here's mine,I was on a family vacation to Aruba about two years ago,and I just bought a new bathing suit.Me and my dad decided to go over to the pool.There was a diving board,and I love diving...I took a jump head first...And off flew my bathing suit. :eek:
IT SUCKED btw...
